(128, '_transient_dash_88ae138922fe95674369b1cb3d215a2b', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/10/wordpress-4-4-beta-2/''>WordPress 4.4 Beta 2</a> <span class="rss-date">October 28, 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">WordPress 4.4 Beta 2 is now available for download and testing. This is software still in development, so we don’t recommend that you run it on a production site. To get the beta, try the WordPress Beta Tester plugin (you’ll want “bleeding edge nightlies”). Or you can download the beta here (zip). For more of what’s new in version 4.4, check out [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/how-non-developers-can-contribute-to-and-influence-wordpress-core-development''>WPTavern: How Non-Developers Can Contribute to and Influence WordPress Core Development</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/daniel-bachhuber-raises-more-than-17-5k-to-develop-a-restful-wp-cli''>WPTavern: Daniel Bachhuber Raises More Than $17.5K to Develop a RESTful WP-CLI</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/93digital-publishes-wordpress-time-machine''>WPTavern: 93Digital Publishes WordPress Time Machine</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Popular Plugin:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/siteorigin-panels/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Page Builder by SiteOrigin</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=siteorigin-panels&amp;_wpnonce=2df4d8d0f4&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Page Builder by SiteOrigin''>Install</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
